dct_description_sm: Engraved by: H. Mol Schulp. (lower left).
Title cartouche is simple frame (bottom, near center).
Includes: California 1., D. d'Anien, M. Vermeille; Iapon, D. de Vriez, and Terra de Jesso to northwest; and 1. de Salomon and N. Zeland to southwest.

Issued in: A New systeme of the mathematicks containing ... a new geography or a discription of the most eminent countries and coasts of the World /Jonas Moore. - London: Printed for Robert Scott, 1681.
